   - A) A president
   - B) A civil rights leader
   - C) A famous inventor
   - D) A professional athlete

10. What holiday is celebrated on the fourth Thursday in November in the United States?
    - A) Halloween
    - B) Independence Day
    - C) Thanksgiving
    - D) Veterans Day

